column5: Are you allready to scrape your wife off the ceiling?  Regards, Snowball

You'd need to have two response teams, if you were to pull that on me. The paramedics to get me to the hospital after the heart attack. Then an industrial clean up crew to clean the butt spray off the walls. LOL But I did have a good laugh at the thought of getting a couple of my buddies this year at the fish camp.  Dan.
